Adult.description: Canada Geese are larger with a larger bill and a longer neck than Cackling Geese, but beware of smaller Canada Geese that approach the size of Cackling. Canada Geese also have a rounder head with a sloping forehead as opposed to a steep forehead seen on Cackling.

Adult (Atlantic).description: Brant lack the white chin strap of a Cackling Goose. The breast is also darker than a Cackling Goose.

Adult (Black).description: Brant lack the white chin strap seen on a Cackling Goose. The breast is also darker than a Cackling Goose.
